Title : John Hayward (stained glass maker)
Text : {{Other people|John Hayward}}
{{Refimprove|date=May 2018}}
'''John David Hayward''' (1929&ndash;2007) was a [[United Kingdom|British]] [[stained glass]] artist who made nearly 200 windows in churches and cathedrals across Britain and abroad.<ref>[http://www.stmichaelslondonfields.org.uk/history/ History | St Michael and All Angels, London Fields<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>

